                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370227-901-offence-1 t18370227-cd-165"></join>5th of February</rs>, 1 bag, value 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 601bs. weight of nails, value 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; and 31bs. weight of copper, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18370227-name-1345" type="victimName">
